SBLIM Base Instrumentation for CMPI README

The Base Instrumentation allows to get information about the system
itself via CIMOM .


Prerequisites are : 

- CIM Schema Version 2.7.1 (preliminary)
- CMPI : Common Manageablity Programming Interface


Base Instrumentation specific libraries :

- CimBase ... implements the resource access and is responsible
  for data gathering 
- cimprovsup ... implements tool functionality to write generic 
  CMPI Provider


Linux Base Schema : 

- mof/Linux_Base.mof


Instrumentation Libraries :

- cmpiLinux_ComputerSystem.c
- cmpiLinux_OperatingSystem.c
- cmpiLinux_Process.c
- cmpiLinux_Processor.c

- cmpiLinux_RunningOS.c
- cmpiLinux_OSProcess.c
- cmpiLinux_CSProcessor.c


Test Script :

semantictest_OSBaseStage1.sh
semantictest_OSBaseStage2_Processor.sh













